{"tid":1742024,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[香城Online 職業一覽] 打機點可以唔升lev","createTime":"2019-11-20T15:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T05:13:16.000Z","uid":150065,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"247973b49bc286cd8ec9f4d8d1237a2b66d372a0","tid":1742024,"uid":150065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:03:12.000Z","msg":"香城online 出咗五個月，越黎越多新職業解鎖，等級上限亦都越黎越高。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">當然d怪亦都越黎越勁...所以大家再停留喺新手階段只會越黎越難打</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小弟喺度整咗個list，大概幫唔同職業分咗星等，10星最高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">玩咗一段時間嘅玩家冇理由仲係停留喺新手階段</span></span>，希望大家都可以好似其他online game 咁，越黎越高lev，甚至解鎖到尚未發掘嘅職業<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">另外隨住敵人嘅變化，希望玩家都可以搵到新模式同戰術應對。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下面嘅職業只限街頭主線仼務，其他副本例如網絡戰線並冇包括在內<br />\n<br />\n<ins>新手區域</ins><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">冷氣軍師</span><br />\n不值一提，有咁多好idea 又唔見你落場指揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">平民</span> ⭐️<br />\n做仼時淨係跟大隊，一般都係行行企企嗌下口號，甚至有時冇意識留意現場環境，一聽到有犬隻出沒就會跑走(even 係流料都會跑咗先)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>和班非系職業進化方向</ins><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">人工屏障</span> ⭐️<br />\n落雨時開遮比有需要玩家<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">輸送員</span> ⭐️⭐️<br />\n組人鏈遞物資上前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">街坊</span> ⭐️⭐️<br />\n掩護徹退玩家、比衫玩家做完仼換、提供暫時shelter<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">哨</span> ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️<br />\n去主戰區附近位置睇下有冇狗車，同埋搵安全撤離路線<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">推廣大使</span> ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️<br />\n痴文宣、裝飾鋪頭<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">畫家</span> ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️<br />\n為馬路牆壁鏡頭噴上美麗圖案<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">物資補給</span> ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️<br />\n食水、急救、文具、魔法材料...<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">車手</span> ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️<br />\n接仔女、送物資<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>活動搞手</strong></span> ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️<br />\nTG 當值Admin、幫手搞唔同event、集會etc<br />\n<br />\n<ins>勇武系職業進化方向</ins><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">工程師</span> ⭐️⭐️⭐️<br />\n起路障、設防線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">結界師</span> ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️<br />\n封印黨鐵同馬路<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">消防員</span> ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️<br />\n滅煙、淋彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">裝修師傅</span> ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️<br />\n翻新黑鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">普通投擲師</span><br />\n地面投擲仼何硬物<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">空投師</span> ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️<br />\n高空投擲仼何硬物<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">魔法師</span> ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️<br />\n火、水、土...仲有好多元素等大家發掘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">弓箭手</span> ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">空投魔法師</span> ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️<br />\n高空投擲各魔法，個人認為暫時最被低估嘅職業之一<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">魔法弓箭手</span> ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️<br />\n箭頭可以溝埋各種魔法，大大提升魔法嘅效用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> so far 見過火陷箭<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">屠龍者</span> ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️<br />\n暫時好少玩家去到呢個lev<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去到呢個level 嘅玩家，你喺遊戲嘅付出真係好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>其他專屬職業</ins><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">記者</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">First-aid</span><br />\n<br />\n如果我有咩職業漏咗，歡迎各位玩家指出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上述只屬遊戲情節，如有雷同，實屬巧合"},{"pid":"43df8ee7f07e338c35c0645bcd0426553481e16c","tid":1742024,"uid":150065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:04:03.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"e8cbf049c94e1b0c945a94e41f7d9c28663f0e5f","tid":1742024,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:04:10.000Z","msg":"借過位<br />\n[多圖]11.21 曙光行動2.0，721 4.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1741920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1741920</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"21063e80009457b526af99dbc9d4cd054bdf1d26","tid":1742024,"uid":150065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:04:26.000Z","msg":"全民都要升lev"},{"pid":"95f80ebd989dd2cd4880400c1ab67f482e9d3978","tid":1742024,"uid":258566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:04:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e7d91fb03a48308c5cae05b5396c5a244306cfa","tid":1742024,"uid":150065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95f80ebd989dd2cd4880400c1ab67f482e9d3978","tid":1742024,"uid":258566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:04:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:04:51.000Z","msg":"emoji 黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56645276b37517cdf05983e400996f1b77052324","tid":1742024,"uid":150065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:05:23.000Z","msg":"同意請轉發"},{"pid":"693f45ef785c910e28e76c384c6adc11d089e83c","tid":1742024,"uid":113360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:05:51.000Z","msg":"我要課金做vip15<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a056412cd97dfb99a42e677a7c3982ff6fc286","tid":1742024,"uid":150065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:05:57.000Z","msg":"快d推上熱門"},{"pid":"a4678515a55b4d7b7cdd5b4ef9edaabef17e7da0","tid":1742024