sg":"人呢 定呢隻game 已經唔再hit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5399ae171db75a3db4c1f0388b0612f1da8242","tid":1742024,"uid":150065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:14:37.000Z","msg":"冇玩家想升lev?"},{"pid":"31e4afcd21ea7feb6fe854a1b6197d9bb180b414","tid":1742024,"uid":256505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:15:09.000Z","msg":"和理非唔知點抗爭？唔想放棄？<br />\n入黎進修下啦<br />\n<br />\n［進擊的和理非］<br />\n和理非武裝化 - 知識篇 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/eyJDKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/eyJDKT</a>"},{"pid":"964c098ef9eae17caae768a7bc830ee403021dff","tid":1742024,"uid":150065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:15:20.000Z","msg":"大家係要升lev<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}